<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Enquiry Reminder - Blue Sky</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 26px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 40px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #007BFF;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #fff4e5;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #FFA500;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 15px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Blue Sky</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p><strong>Hello <%= buyer_name %>,</strong></p>

      <p>We noticed that your enquiry <strong>#<%= enquiry_id %></strong>, expiring on <strong><%= expiry_date %></strong>, has not received any quotes from suppliers.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <p>To increase your chances of receiving relevant quotations, we recommend upgrading your plan to <strong>BSO Admin</strong>.</p>
      </div>

      <p>Upgrading ensures better visibility and response from suppliers who are aligned with your requirements.</p>

      <a href="<%= plan_change_url %>" class="btn">Upgrade My Plan</a>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team anytime.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br><strong>Blue Sky Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Blue Sky. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
